    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >食材在空中飞舞，AI来做料理！？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家只需用剑切割食材。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个非常简单的VR动作游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >同时切割食材！新鲜度UP喵！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果能同时切割3个食材，料理的质量会提升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作独一无二的料理！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据切割的食材，每次完成的料理都不同，让人上瘾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用ChatGPT的图像生成AI会构思原创料理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >将完成的料理发布到SNS上吧！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成的料理看起来美味吗？还是有点奇特的神秘料理？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发布到SNS上，与朋友们一起分享乐趣吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你也想拿起剑，与猫咪们一起享受奇幻料理吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/30b71c446ac062717943c015e5ade826.avif?t=1733391745\" width=620 height=155 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/7fc0cc5f90326528249fe73865c1e296.avif?t=1733391745\" width=620 height=155 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/73b49bceff84f7a700745a7b392c9430.avif?t=1733391745\" width=620 height=155 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >评论模式新登场！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用符合评审口味的食材制作料理吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剑客厨师技能将受到评价。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/7c6b24856e62db3d7ebf2ad836941c23.avif?t=1733391745\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras_big/7c6b24856e62db3d7ebf2ad836941c23.avif?t=1733391745 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VR上的操作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/9b7f2d146cf10e9840aab37c02c28206.avif?t=1733391745\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras_big/9b7f2d146cf10e9840aab37c02c28206.avif?t=1733391745 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PC上的操作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/e0ba9196741f75fbcbd816793ea2747f.avif?t=1733391745\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras_big/e0ba9196741f75fbcbd816793ea2747f.avif?t=1733391745 width=800 height=200 /></span></p>",
